name: HUMAN (Music By Imam Kikou)
description:
We are all the same human beings with the same potential to be a good or bad human being but in no way are we the same. There is a story behind each and everyone of us, a reason why we are the way we are. Think! before you judge!

My Collaborative work with Imam Kikou. Get another piece on Imam Kikou’s OBJKT Account @SekudBeat.

DM the transaction proof to Imam Kikou's Twitter for the full song ; https://twitter.com/SakauImam
